IZAKHAMUZI zaseMganduzweni ngaseWhite River zishise imizi yabasolwa abathinteka ecaleni lokubulawa kukaBontle Mashiyane. Izikhamuzi ziqale emzini wesangoma okuthiwa yisona esitholakale nezicubu zomzimba kaBontle. Isangoma esishiselwe umuzi sisolwa ngokuthi asiqali ukuthuma abasolwa ukuba bathole zicubu zezingane. Imibiko ezungeza ezinkundleni ngokwe-video okukholakala ukuthi ingeyomunye wabasolwa, okunguyena oveze imininingwane ngezicubu zikaBontle, iveze ukuthi akayona ingane yokuqala ukubulawa ikhishwe izicubu zomzimba. Umuzi wesibili oshisiwe ngowakamakhelwane naye oboshelwe leli cala nalowo okukholakala ukuthi yisoka lakhe. 